{"actor":"sashakile","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T12:54:21Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":55,"issue_id":"sxAct-f7q","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"sxAct-f7q\",\"title\":\"Implement snapshot regeneration workflow (xact-test regen-oracle)\",\"description\":\"Implement the xact-test regen-oracle --diff command that regenerates oracle snapshots and displays a diff before overwriting. Workflow: (1) run all test files against the live oracle, (2) compare new outputs to existing snapshots in oracle/, (3) display changed/added/removed tests with a readable diff, (4) prompt for confirmation before writing. Required for maintaining snapshot freshness when xAct version or Wolfram version changes. Reference specs/2026-01-22-design-framework-gaps.md Sprint 3 item 11.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":3,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"saxa.kile@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-23T17:40:57Z\",\"created_by\":\"sashakile\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-23T17:45:07Z\"}"}
